<td class="tableblock halign-left valign-top"><p class="tableblock">A link with the container <strong>Checkout: Override payment method</strong> replaces all previous payment methods with the PayPal PLUS Wall.  Any payment methods offered in addition to those included in the Wall – PayPal, Debit and Credit card – are displayed below these four inside the wall in the order of their priority.<br>
In the assistant, different options how to display the PayPal PLUS Wall are available: <strong>Wall replaces the payment list</strong>, <strong>Wall within the payment list</strong> or <strong>Wall in an overlay during the purchase</strong>.<br>
