<td class="icon">
<i class="fa icon-tip" title="Tip"></i>
</td>
<td class="content">
<div class="title">Change visibility</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p>You can use the visibility to restrict who can read the messages of an issue. At first all issues are visible to every user. The visibility can only be restricted after the first message has been received. The setting applies to all messages of an issue.</p>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
</tbody></table>
</div>
